I've seen my fair share of NTR on this site, and I gotta, this ain't it. A lot more of the story is devoted to the girl and almost none to the guy getting "cucked" Hell, he doesn't have eyes, a definite sign of an unimportant character. A good, well written NTR would devote time to the relationship between the girl and the guy, (as well as maybe giving him eyes) only to pull the rug from underneath the reader and then show how the girl betrays her love, falling into pleasure with the bull leaving the poor guy, well, cucked. Here, you get none of that. The reader isn't given a reason to care about the cuck and that doesn't make for a good NTR. The only thing good here is the art and the girl. I may not like NTR as a genre, but I know the difference between a good and bad story.
